  "label": "Severan Duskmar",
  "description": "This individual is an undead human of spare, sinew-bared build, preserved in the rigid desiccation typical of long interment. Light skin clings tight to the facial planes, with a collapsed nasal bridge and exposed dentition that fixes the features in a permanent rictus. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets beneath pronounced brow ridges, giving an unblinking, funerary stare. Black hair survives in uneven, brittle strands along the scalp, breaking into patchy lengths that never fully cover the bone-knotted crown.",
